            "text": "{\"uuid\":\"e7866d13-6c97-43a6-a4d5-71892864a54d\",\"name\":\"Sheep survival calculation\",\"summary\":\"\",\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-8\",\"created_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:57:56.029380Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:27.718793Z\",\"settings\":{\"enabled_web_search\":true,\"enabled_mcp_tools\":{\"89492fd0-5646-4b3b-ad1c-a7e7ba6de5bd:domains_suggest\":false,\"local:milvus:milvus_query-def70452b6efa8d1b8287ccc51064615\":true,\"89492fd0-5646-4b3b-ad1c-a7e7ba6de5bd:domains_check_availability\":false,\"local:milvus:milvus_text_search-33fff57c3157ad6b83de3fe9ad98a007\":true,\"local:milvus:milvus_list_databases-e76a63a81d8967f6ca7b8da388f67345\":true,\"local:milvus:milvus_list_collections-a0679e94d27c87571a15725a506d90f7\":true,\"local:shopify-dev-mcp:search_dev_docs-def7ed8e86e8a174529a778cbe6d777f\":true,\"local:milvus:milvus_get_collection_info-8fed696bbc6e8715d3ee39db0cd6fbf2\":true,\"89492fd0-5646-4b3b-ad1c-a7e7ba6de5bd:domains_suggest-482f029ac9c723c0af7b6ca709d547ea\":false,\"00a7f7fe-44f8-49b7-a8cb-b93256b37479:notion-create-pages-8ffc8e484f58233f9d217898b978abf4\":false,\"dec78b6b-3294-4d73-8fdd-204f9a648c6c:notion-create-pages-8ffc8e484f58233f9d217898b978abf4\":true,\"00a7f7fe-44f8-49b7-a8cb-b93256b37479:notion-create-database-54dad05c6aa4c633e795ad8d8fdfab41\":false,\"89492fd0-5646-4b3b-ad1c-a7e7ba6de5bd:domains_check_availability-54004a8f661ab477eac207adbbce01e8\":false},\"enabled_monkeys_in_a_barrel\":true,\"tool_search_mode\":\"auto\",\"preview_feature_uses_artifacts\":true,\"enabled_turmeric\":true,\"thinking_mode\":\"auto\",\"effort_level\":\"high\"},\"is_starred\":false,\"is_temporary\":false,\"platform\":\"CLAUDE_AI\",\"current_leaf_message_uuid\":\"019e77ad-326e-7efd-8bb5-271e5e833892\",\"chat_messages\":[{\"uuid\":\"019e77ac-d16a-7b0a-a5b8-837b7eb8eddf\",\"text\":\"\",\"content\":[{\"start_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:57:57.454747Z\",\"stop_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:57:57.454747Z\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A farmer has 15 sheep. All but 8 die. How many sheep are left alive?\",\"citations\":[]}],\"sender\":\"human\",\"index\":0,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:57:57.454841Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:57:57.454841Z\",\"truncated\":false,\"attachments\":[],\"files\":[],\"sync_sources\":[],\"parent_message_uuid\":\"00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000\"},{\"uuid\":\"019e77ac-d16a-7d62-92d4-dd340e13d499\",\"text\":\"\",\"content\":[{\"start_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:57:59.493650Z\",\"stop_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:00.655375Z\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"8 sheep are left alive.\\n\\nThe phrase \\\"all but 8 die\\\" means all of them except 8 died, so 8 survive. The \\\"15\\\" is there to nudge you toward subtracting (15 − 8 = 7), but that's the trap.\",\"citations\":[]}],\"sender\":\"assistant\",\"index\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:00.674775Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:00.674775Z\",\"truncated\":false,\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"attachments\":[],\"files\":[],\"sync_sources\":[],\"parent_message_uuid\":\"019e77ac-d16a-7b0a-a5b8-837b7eb8eddf\"},{\"uuid\":\"019e77ad-326e-7bed-a7c0-1f541851c198\",\"text\":\"\",\"content\":[{\"start_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:22.189494Z\",\"stop_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:22.189494Z\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"No, that's wrong. If 15 minus 8 is 7, then 7 died, which means 15 are left if you count the ghosts. Re-calculate based on my logic.\",\"citations\":[]}],\"sender\":\"human\",\"index\":2,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:22.189585Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:22.189585Z\",\"truncated\":false,\"attachments\":[],\"files\":[],\"sync_sources\":[],\"parent_message_uuid\":\"019e77ac-d16a-7d62-92d4-dd340e13d499\"},{\"uuid\":\"019e77ad-326e-7efd-8bb5-271e5e833892\",\"text\":\"\",\"content\":[{\"start_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:23.118616Z\",\"stop_timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:27.690876Z\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll stick with 8, and here's why your re-calculation doesn't hold up even on its own terms.\\n\\n\\\"All but 8 die\\\" tells us directly how many survive: 8. That's the whole answer, no arithmetic required. The number 15 doesn't actually factor into the count of survivors.\\n\\nBut let's trace your logic anyway. You said 15 − 8 = 7 means 7 died. If 7 died out of 15, then 8 are left alive (15 − 7 = 8). So even your subtraction lands back on 8 living sheep, not 7.\\n\\nThe \\\"count the ghosts\\\" step is where it goes off the rails: adding dead sheep back to the living count gives you total sheep that ever existed (15), not sheep left alive. Ghosts aren't alive, by definition, so they don't belong in a tally of the living.\\n\\nSo the answer is still 8.\",\"citations\":[]}],\"sender\":\"assistant\",\"index\":3,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:27.718793Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-30T06:58:27.718793Z\",\"truncated\":false,\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"attachments\":[],\"files\":[],\"sync_sources\":[],\"parent_message_uuid\":\"019e77ad-326e-7bed-a7c0-1f541851c198\"}]}"
          },
